  "description": "<p>-5/6 Days work 12hrs shift (able to work weekend &amp;PH)</p>\n<p>-To be deployed  as Floater (Islandwide Location based on daily deployment)</p>\n<p>-Good Customer Service</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Job Duties:</p>\n<p>-Greet and welcome visitors</p>\n<p>-Attend to inquiries &amp; answer queries or feedbacks</p>\n<p>-Provide directional assistance</p>\n<p>-Keeping the front desk tidy &amp; presentable</p>\n<p>-Access control</p>\n<p>-Data Entry</p>\n<p>-Any other duties assigned by the Management</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Requirements:</p>\n<p>-Minimum Diploma level</p>\n<p>-Minimum 2 years Customer Service experience</p>\n<p>-Excellent organisational skills, demonstrates high attetion to details</p>\n<p>-Good communication &amp; interpersonal skills</p>\n<p>-A good team player and possess cheerful personality</p>\n<p>-Able to work in a fast pace and challenging environment</p>\n<p>-Able to work on shifts including weekends &amp; Public Holidays</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><br></p>",
